        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-05-22 14:11:15.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nwhy prepare-docker would install docker?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "9f173cd75f8b46aee4104146cc27e0060f3d54e2",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 5019,
          "name": "Michal Zegan",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "m.zegan@samsung.com",
          "username": "m.zegan"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-05-22 14:23:28.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> why prepare-docker would install docker?\n\nin case of docker role it doesn't have to, but docker role doesn't know which version it takes unless it works offline because there it has the exactly specified version that was put into resources.tar. I believe that prepare-docker installing docker with version selection won't help in that case",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "7a464663d9f3af8a1981c405ce7cc2b717234ce6",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3957,
          "name": "Samuli Silvius",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "s.silvius@partner.samsung.com",
          "username": "silvius"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-05-22 16:28:30.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> > Patch Set 1:\n> > \n> > why prepare-docker would install docker?\n> \n> in case of docker role it doesn't have to, but docker role doesn't know which version it takes unless it works offline because there it has the exactly specified version that was put into resources.tar. I believe that prepare-docker installing docker with version selection won't help in that case\n\nI don't get it:) In which case prepare-role would install docker?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "40f1c8ae8d41bd745070cfbf9a54b8792e042cf1",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 5097,
          "name": "Bartek Grzybowski",
